# Changelog

## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.6] - 2026-04-01

## [1.0.5] - 2026-04-01

- Switched release packaging to Pixi-based bundles instead of PyInstaller.
- Added top-level launcher wrappers that activate the bundled runtime before starting `geodepot`.
- Added POSIX and PowerShell installer scripts for downloading and installing release bundles.
- Updated the user-facing install and release docs for the new bundle layout and installer flow.
- Consolidated developer recipes around Pixi and `just`, and removed the old PyInstaller experiment files.

## [1.0.0] - TBD

First release.
